short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An augmented OpenSea experience powered by LuckyTrader, including mass bidding, mass listing, and rarity data.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Expedite the buying and selling process on OpenSea with the Lucky Trader extension. With the extension installed, rarity data will be automatically augmented on asset cards for supported NFT collections, and users can mass bid and mass list NFTs in a few clicks.
